{"tid":2302055,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"2000年-2010十大華語神曲你識幾多首? 當年港台樂壇好撚屈機","createTime":"2020-11-26T23:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T14:41:03.000Z","uid":353419,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb25d4b964e388d705231e10f0c36c479ddfa0f9","tid":2302055,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:35:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">10.蔡依琳- 七十二變</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>呢首係2003年既Online Game主題曲，小學果陣一路打機一路聽，果個年代網路唔算發達，我係戀愛盒子識左個台灣仔網戀老公，台灣人唔興MSN同ICQ，佢地用Yahoo Messager，有次老公由台灣打電話比我傾計，好記得佢問我: 「你喜歡蔡依琳嗎? 」<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B94n5Lbj4aw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB94n5Lbj4aw&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=985d2039\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B94n5Lbj4aw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">9.楊丞琳 - 曖昧</span><br />\n<br />\n2006年果陣，楊丞琳紅到癲，台劇惡魔在身邊好好睇，當年租碟鋪仲未絕跡，BT仲係好慢，Youtube功能仲係好原始，我全套50集租左翻屋企睇，睇左成個暑假<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mebzXfWi87E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmebzXfWi87E&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=d1b1e810\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mebzXfWi87E</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">8. Twins- 眼紅紅</span><br />\n<br />\n我小學三年班果陣已經好渴望拍拖，大慨俾Twins既歌影響左，佢地啲青春電影都好紅，例如係千機變，這個夏天有異性，絕種鐵金剛，有次美術堂暗戀既男同學教第二個女同學做勞作，我傷心夜晚係床瘋狂用MP3 聽Twins既歌，當年Mp3得32Mb，大約得8首歌，聽到果句「人人懷念他，一起去學結他」 諗起佢地甜蜜畫面， 我即刻爆喊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y5dgQWqw2qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY5dgQWqw2qg&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=429fefd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y5dgQWqw2qg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">7.  潘瑋柏x弦子 ---不得不愛</span><br />\n<br />\n大約2007-2009年左右，中學生好興去網吧，每次去網吧就會聽到呢首歌，因為好多女仔打緊勁舞團，當年MSN狀態可以顯示聽緊咩歌，成日都見到呢首歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gUgOKdZ1tbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgUgOKdZ1tbk&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=a3470259\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gUgOKdZ1tbk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">6.周杰倫- 龍捲風</span><br />\n<br />\n未有智能手機之前，大家好興用手機鈴聲，當年我同男朋友曖昧緊，果陣未正式成為戀人，但肯定遲早一齊既感覺真係好正，我特定整左佢專用鈴聲係龍捲風，每次響起「愛情來得太快就像龍捲風」，我就知係佢打比我，後來覺得太煩，頂唔順轉左首歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPWDeLqsN0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRPWDeLqsN0g&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=b5b9021b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPWDeLqsN0g</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">5.羅志祥- 潮男正傳</span><br />\n<br />\n中學生開始會打扮追潮流，羅志祥又係潮流指標之一，聽呢首歌好有共嗚，呢首歌MTV入面出現左好多當時好興既造型，其中一個就係恤衫打呔，當年既MK指定造型，無論男女都好鐘意恤衫打呔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_XP0OL70SA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN_XP0OL70SA&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=f0e785df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_XP0OL70SA</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">4.鄧麗欣 -  電燈膽</span><br />\n<br />\n2005-2008年左右， 每逢去唱K一定有人點方力申鄧麗欣，一來好易唱，二來佢地既葉念琛三部曲電影既中學生既聖經，但唯獨呢首電燈膽真係好撚難唱，當年鄧麗欣出左名唱呢首走音，但唔好話佢本人，連我地成班同學都唱到走哂音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kX0ED_mQJto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkX0ED_mQJto&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=28d0c58c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kX0ED_mQJto</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">3.當四葉草碰上劍尖時 - Shining Friends</span><br />\n<br />\n呢首歌係神劇既主題曲， 03年果陣每逢夜晚十點就會播，果陣我一路打彩虹冒險，一路ICQ跟同學傾計，一路睇呢套劇，入面啲景靚到呢，一直唔覺原來係香港黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i3ejfEN4waA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di3ejfEN4waA&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=066793e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i3ejfEN4waA</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">2.衛蘭----大哥</span><br />\n<br />\n06年果陣，衛蘭係香港最紅既女歌手，果陣好多人用FOXY 下載佢啲MTV，佢啲歌全部都係講做兵，其實我想講女仔都會做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，果陣暗戀個男仔，成日當我工人咁洗，打古龍俾人格殺要我救佢，又要帶佢去狂屍洞幫佢吸經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WgNkhzW7iFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWgNkhzW7iFU&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=5acffde7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WgNkhzW7iFU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">1周杰倫【說好的幸福呢</span><br />\n<br />\n呢首未必係周杰倫最高水準之作, 但算係佢係香港最紅時期出既歌, 果陣成個XANGA都係呢首背景音樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mLFhTFiX0uM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmLFhTFiX0uM&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=3ddcbf6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mLFhTFiX0uM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹係我心目中既TOP10, 唔知大家心目中既TOP 10係咩呢? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"61707d5b55fb5ca091f514723f7c11d319e8cd97","tid":2302055,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:42:32.000Z","msg":"點解電燈膽個mv 係十分愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261a9ce9e73570e9e99bc36cd98f23ff4e7656ec","tid":2302055,"uid":308569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"FIR 我們的愛"},{"pid":"26ef641f564b170